            <p>Hi, I'm Mariana! ⭐️ A Digital Product Designer based in Lisbon, exploring the intersection of people,
              systems, and design. With a background in Communication Design, I approach problems through a critical and
              socially engaged lens. I'm drawn to environments where dialogue, collaboration, and open critique push
              ideas further.</p>

            <p>Naturally introspective and observant, I listen closely. This quiet attention helps me surface deeper
              insights and navigate ambiguity with care. I'm driven by curiosity and imagination, often connecting ideas
              across disciplines. I design with heart as much as with logic. Empathy is a constant guide in my process,
              leading me toward accessible, inclusive, and user-centered outcomes. At the same time, I remain adaptable
              and open to change, trusting the process of exploration and iteration to uncover the right direction.</p>

          </div>

